ox tail

preheat oven 220, and caramelise the 1 kg oxtail with glug of oil for 20 min
meanwhile, 1 leek halved and chunked into 2cm pieces, 4 carrots -> 2 cm pieces into medium heat, add thyme, rosemary, 2 bay.
Remove oxtail, set to 170C, add 2 cloves, 1 heaped tbsp flour, 1 tin plum tomatoes, 150 ml red wine, 0.5 l stock,

Cook 5 hours, add worcestershire sauce. stirring hourly, splash of water if necc.plE890
